(1, 1, 'A WordPress Commenter', 'wapuu@wordpress.example', 'https://wordpress.org/', '', '2020-06-15 18:31:36', '2020-06-15 18:31:36', 'Hi, this is a comment.\nTo get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard.\nCommenter avatars come from <a href=\"https://gravatar.com\">Gravatar</a>.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(2, 2838, 'Lisa Rico', 'LisaRico@gmail.com', '', '42.201.169.192', '2018-05-07 11:23:14', '2018-05-07 11:23:14', 'Cameron Alley  is amazing, great teacher, mentor and such amazing individual. The dance academy offers youth classes  hard to find, great summer dance camp and positive environment to hav kids after school. love that dancing moves.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(3, 2846, 'http://canadianorderpharmacy.com/', 'fghserf@bigmir.net', '', '31.184.238.111', '2019-06-04 00:10:49', '2019-06-04 00:10:49', 'Awesome post.', 0, '0', '', '', 0, 0),
(4, 2581, 'mike', 'mike@gmail.com', '', '180.178.145.28', '2018-03-13 10:47:09', '2018-03-13 10:47:09', 'We are here for our third anniversary and everything was great. The wine our waiter chose was excellent, the charcuterie chefs selection was delicious and the filet mignon was perfect! It comes at a cost but it’s very worth it. Less expensive than other places in New York for so much more. I’d eat here again without question. I love this place.', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
(5, 2581, 'Melisa', 'Melisa@gmail.com', '', '180.178.145.28', '2018-03-13 10:49:35', '2018-03-13 10:49:35', 'The restaurant is not that big that we expect but food and service are great in coming next time 100%.', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
(6, 2662, 'Lisa Rico', 'LisaRico@gmail.com', '', '180.178.145.28', '2018-03-13 07:42:45', '2018-03-13 07:42:45', 'If you are into Yoga and/or Meditation i would like to suggest do not go there. they are ultra expensive. The location and views are stunning. Beautiful landscaped walking trail and breathtaking view from the summit but message services are too high. You have to experience it for yourself. Super expensive so unless you earn in US Dollars, you cannot take their services. Still a great experience to wander around.', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
(7, 2662, 'Alex', 'Alex@gmail.com', '', '180.178.145.28', '2018-03-13 09:16:27', '2018-03-13 09:16:27', 'These guys are the BEST!! As a woman, it is hard sometimes to find a place that doesn\'t take advantage of that-this is not \"that kind of place.\" GREAT work at beyond a fair price. HIGHLY recommend!', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
(8, 2669, 'Melisa', 'Melisa@gmail.com', '', '180.178.143.22', '2018-03-12 11:53:43', '2018-03-12 11:53:43', 'BBQ Jackfruit Pizza has the best pizza in New York. Their sauce is freshly made and topped with the finest Mozzarella chesse and customer service is tops. This is my davorite pizza place in town!', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
(9, 2669, 'mike', 'mike@gmail.com', '', '180.178.145.28', '2018-03-13 08:09:48', '2018-03-13 08:09:48', 'I would love to tell everyone how amazing the pizzas were! Unfortunately I cannot as we never made it to a table. We had read about ‘stoking of oven’ between 3.15 and 4pm so timed our visit accordingly. After a lovely walk over Brooklyn Bridge in the cold, we arrived 7 minutes before 4pm. We asked if we could come in perhaps and get a drink; only to be told we could wait within the plastic covered porch area. At 1 minute to 4 I once again entered the restaurant to ask if we could now come in. This time the response was; “I have to speak to my manager”. I was astonished not just by the treatment but the whole approach to us as potential customers of their establishment. We told them that we had no desire to give them our custom and departed. I very much doubt this review will affect their business but as overseas visitors we certainly won’t be recommending BBQ Jackfruit Pizza!', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
(10, 2682, 'mike', 'mike@gmail.com', '', '180.178.145.28', '2018-03-13 07:59:03', '2018-03-13 07:59:03', 'I have been a member of many gyms in my many years on this planet...nothing compares to the J’s Big Gym... its one of those hidden treasures not too many people know about. Indoor and outdoor pools, 24 hour gym, basketball, racquetball, indoor track, hot tubs, steam and sauna rooms...its more than just a gym...', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
(11, 2682, 'Melisa', 'Melisa@gmail.com', '', '180.178.145.28', '2018-03-13 09:07:33', '2018-03-13 09:07:33', 'The fitness center was good. You just signed in and used the machines there. There was a row of elliptical type machines, a row of treadmills and some weight machines. Nothing fancy but it worked! I got a 2 day pass to the spa. I did not get any treatments but I did hear women chatting in there about how great their treatments were. There was never anyone else in there so I got it to myself. I used the showers which were nice as well. I might book a treatment next time and the spa facilities would be included.', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
(12, 2710, 'Alex', 'Alex@gmail.com', '', '180.178.143.22', '2018-03-12 12:52:34', '2018-03-12 12:52:34', 'Wow! Visited for a Thursday brunch with my family and we were so pleasantly surprised at the great service, high quality food! We will definitely return! Huge mimosas. delicious food!!', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
(13, 2710, 'mike', 'mike@gmail.com', '', '180.178.145.28', '2018-03-13 08:17:17', '2018-03-13 08:17:17', 'Always a fun place to have lunch! Excellent food and service in a truly unique atmosphere. The staff was very accommodating to our young child’s request. Love all the salads. I tried the beet salad with shrimp. Absolutely delicious combination!', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
(14, 73, 'Lisa Rico', 'LisaRico@gmail.com', '', '42.201.169.192', '2018-05-08 13:44:02', '2018-05-08 13:44:02', 'I love the simplistic design of the watch, it has a modern feel because of the gold on black yet is slightly rustic because of the leather.\nThe glass also tints to an aqua blue when the light hits it at a certain angle - a really neat extra feature.', 0, '1', '', 'review', 0, 0),
